ing: 1 (15 ounce) can black beans with green chilies, drained
1 (10 ounce) can diced tomatoes with green chilies, drained
n: Bachelors Flamin' Hot Mexican Bean Dip
des: "This is a great dip for block parties, office parties, football parties..lots of parties!  Its hot and easy, not to mention quick."
ins: Heat the olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat. Add onion and garlic; cook and stir until onion is translucent, about 5 minutes. Pour in the jalapenos, black beans, diced tomatoes with green chilies and cheese dip. Heat through, stirring to blend as needed. Serve hot.
